Add_Dynamic_Module Physics Test_Physics
Physics Debug 1
Physics Set_Paths ./Resources
Physics List_Plugins
Physics Set_Load_Mode Manual
Physics Use Player Default
Physics Set_Body_Type Player Character
Physics Set Player Mass 80
Physics Set_Position Player 0.0 1.0 2.0
Physics Set_Velocity Player 0.0 0.0 0.0
Physics Apply_Force Player 0.0 -9.8 0.0
Physics Apply_Impulse Player 1.0 0.0 0.0
Physics Set_Gravity 0.0 -9.8 0.0
Physics Update Player
Physics Update All
Physics Release Player
Physics Set_Plugin_Wanted Default 0
Physics Apply_Load_Plan
Physics List_Plugins
Physics Set_Load_Mode On_Demand
Physics Attach Player Default
Physics Update All
Physics Detach Player
Physics List_Plugins
Done
